          "reading": "Yasui resutoran wo sagashite imasu.",
          "meaning": "I'm looking for a cheap restaurant."
        }
      ],
      "notes": "い-adjectives go directly before nouns without any particle.",
      "difficulty": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "g16_02",
