      "meaning": "Negative form of い-adjectives",
      "formation": "[い-adjective stem] + くない",
      "examples": [
        {
          "japanese": "このほんはたかくないです。",
          "reading": "Kono hon wa takakunai desu.",
          "meaning": "This book is not expensive."
